cleaned_text: [ Dianne M. Fontanez-Nieves, MD, Joins the Department ](https://anest.ufl.edu/2020/06/05/dianne-m-fontanez-nieves-md-joins-the-department/) Dianne M. Fontanez-Nieves, MD, joined us on June 1, 2020, as an Assistant Professor of Anesthesiology in the Division of Multispecialty Anesthesiology. Dr. Fontanez-Nieves was most recently an Associate Consultant in the Department of Anesthesiology at the Mayo Clinic in Rochester, Minnesota.
